---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';

export async function getStaticPaths() {
  const posts = [
    {
      slug: "why-72-21-7-is-best",
      title: "The Science of Comfort: Why 72/21/7 is the Gold Standard",
      date: "April 10, 2026",
      image: "https://sc02.alicdn.com/kf/A0064eeab34cc43ffaad5a0739e62beafC.png",
      keywords: "72% Polyester 21% Rayon 7% Spandex, medical scrub fabric, healthcare uniform material",
      description: "A deep dive into the textile engineering behind the most successful medical scrub brands.",
      content: `
        <p class="mb-8 leading-relaxed">For years, the medical apparel industry was dominated by heavy, stiff cotton. But as shifts became longer and the physical demands on healthcare workers increased, the need for a 'performance gear' approach became evident. At Yilong Scrubs, our research led us to the <strong>72/21/7 Signature Blend.</strong></p>
        <img src="https://sc02.alicdn.com/kf/A0064eeab34cc43ffaad5a0739e62beafC.png" alt="Close-up of premium scrub fabric texture" class="rounded-[2rem] w-full h-[400px] object-cover my-12 shadow-xl" />
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-black mt-16 mb-6 italic text-slate-900">Breaking Down the Gold Ratio</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 my-12">
          <div class="p-6 bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100"><h4 class="font-black text-primary mb-2 italic">72% Polyester</h4><p class="text-sm italic">The Backbone. Provides the structural integrity and durability needed for 50+ industrial washes without fading or pilling.</p></div>
          <div class="p-6 bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100"><h4 class="font-black text-secondary mb-2 italic">21% Rayon</h4><p class="text-sm italic">The Soul. Provides the ultra-soft hand-feel and moisture-wicking properties essential for 12-hour shifts.</p></div>
          <div class="p-6 bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100"><h4 class="font-black text-indigo-600 mb-2 italic">7% Spandex</h4><p class="text-sm italic">The Engine. Delivers the critical 4-way stretch that allows healthcare heroes to move without restriction.</p></div>
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-black mt-16 mb-6 italic text-slate-900">Solving the "Stiffness" Pain Point</h2>
        <p class="mb-8 leading-relaxed italic text-slate-600">The most common complaint from medical professionals is uniforms that restrict movement. By using this specific ratio in our 205GSM Elite series, we've created a garment that performs like athletic wear but looks like high-end professional apparel.</p>
      `
    },
    {
      slug: "future-of-ai-in-manufacturing",
      title: "Smart Factories: AI Transformation in Medical Scrub Production",
      date: "December 15, 2025",
      image: "https://sc02.alicdn.com/kf/A6c9a8add0496444fba0d8ebd8fc6c61cH.png",
      keywords: "AI garment manufacturing, smart factory, medical apparel trends",
      description: "How artificial intelligence is revolutionizing the production of medical scrubs.",
      content: `
        <p class="mb-8 leading-relaxed">As we close out 2025, the 'Slow Response' pain point is being solved by technology. At Yilong Scrubs, we've integrated AI-driven systems into our Anhui facility to ensure we stay ahead of global demand.</p>
        <img src="https://sc02.alicdn.com/kf/A6c9a8add0496444fba0d8ebd8fc6c61cH.png" alt="AI designer creating scrub sketches" class="rounded-[2rem] w-full h-[400px] object-cover my-12 shadow-xl" />
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-black mb-4 italic">Reducing Waste, Increasing Speed</h2>
        <p class="mb-8 leading-relaxed italic">Our new AI pattern-nesting software has reduced fabric waste by 12% and cut our lead times for samples down to just 3 days. For a brand owner, this means faster 'Time-to-Market' and lower production costs without compromising on quality.</p>
      `
    },
    {
      slug: "procurement-for-small-clinics",
      title: "Smart Procurement: Solving the High MOQ Barrier for Clinics",
      date: "June 20, 2025",
      keywords: "clinic procurement, medical uniform wholesale, small clinic scrubs",
      description: "Efficient ways for small medical practices to source high-quality uniforms.",
      content: `<p class='mb-6'>Small medical practices often face the 'High MOQ' pain point. Large factories ignore orders below 500 sets. At Yilong, we've optimized our lines for <strong>10-set MOQs</strong>, allowing clinics to maintain a professional brand identity without the inventory risk.</p>`
    },
    {
      slug: "fabric-science-polyester-vs-rayon",
      title: "Fabric Science: The Battle Between Polyester and Rayon",
      date: "December 10, 2024",
      keywords: "polyester vs rayon, medical apparel fabric, scrubs material science",
      description: "An in-depth look at the fibers that make up your daily work uniform.",
      content: `<p class='mb-6'>Why blend? Polyester offers strength and color-fastness, while Rayon adds the breathability and silk-like touch. In this post, we explain how Yilong's specific weaving technique ensures these fibers work in harmony for all-day comfort.</p>`
    },
    {
      slug: "hospital-color-trends-2024",
      title: "Hospital Color Trends 2024: Beyond the Basic Blue",
      date: "June 15, 2024",
      keywords: "scrub colors, hospital uniform trends, medical fashion 2024",
      description: "Sage Green and Charcoal Grey are taking over healthcare.",
      content: `<p class='mb-6'>Patients respond better to calming, modern palettes. We explore why Sage Green and Burgundy are the top sellers of 2024 and how our reactive-dyeing process keeps them vibrant after 50 washes.</p>`
    },
    {
      slug: "reducing-lead-times-strategy",
      title: "Strategy: How We Reduced Lead Times by 30%",
      date: "December 20, 2023",
      keywords: "manufacturing lead times, scrubs production, efficient sourcing",
      description: "Yilong's commitment to faster delivery for global healthcare brands.",
      content: `<p class='mb-6'>Slow response kills brands. We've optimized our Anhui supply chain to offer 15-30 day bulk delivery. In this post, we detail our vertical integration and how it benefits our international partners.</p>`
    },
    {
      slug: "balancing-cost-and-quality",
      title: "Value Engineering: Balancing Cost and Quality in Scrubs",
      date: "June 10, 2023",
      keywords: "scrubs quality control, cost-effective medical uniforms, factory direct scrubs",
      description: "Don't fall for the trap of cheap, low-quality scrubs.",
      content: `<p class='mb-6'>Low price often means hidden costs in the form of fading and pilling. We explain why investing in high-GSM, 4-way stretch fabric saves brands money by reducing returns and increasing customer loyalty.</p>`
    },
    {
      slug: "branding-your-scrub-startup",
      title: "A Beginner's Guide to Branding Your Scrub Startup",
      date: "December 15, 2022",
      keywords: "start a scrub brand, custom labels, medical apparel branding",
      description: "How to move from generic uniforms to a recognized brand.",
      content: `<p class='mb-6'>Branding is more than a logo. From woven neck labels to custom-branded polybags, Yilong's full OEM/ODM toolkit allows startups to look like established global players from day one.</p>`
    },
    {
      slug: "sustainable-manufacturing-healthcare",
      title: "The Shift Towards Sustainable Healthcare Manufacturing",
      date: "June 25, 2022",
      keywords: "sustainable scrubs, eco-friendly medical apparel, OEKO-TEX certified",
      description: "Why OEKO-TEX certification is the first step toward a greener industry.",
      content: `<p class='mb-6'>Safety is sustainability. By ensuring all Yilong fabrics are OEKO-TEX Standard 100 certified, we protect both the medical professional and the environment from harmful chemical waste.</p>`
    },
    {
      slug: "sourcing-medical-apparel-guide",
      title: "Global Guide: Sourcing Medical Apparel from China",
      date: "December 12, 2021",
      keywords: "source scrubs from China, medical garment factory, wholesale guide",
      description: "Essential tips for international buyers looking for reliable partners.",
      content: `<p class='mb-6'>Middlemen often hide behind factory photos. We provide a 5-point checklist for vetting a true manufacturer, including 100% apparel focus and direct communication channels.</p>`
    },
    {
      slug: "evolution-from-cotton-to-stretch",
      title: "The Evolution: From Boxy Cotton to High-Performance Stretch",
      date: "June 18, 2021",
      keywords: "stretch scrubs, cotton vs spandex, medical uniform history",
      description: "How fabric technology changed the medical uniform.",
      content: `<p class='mb-6'>The days of stiff cotton are over. We look back at how the industry shifted to synthetic 4-way stretch blends and why Spandex became the healthcare worker's best friend.</p>`
    },
    {
      slug: "antimicrobial-fabrics-new-standard",
      title: "2020 Standard: The Surge in Antimicrobial Fabric Demand",
      date: "December 20, 2020",
      keywords: "antimicrobial scrubs, infection control uniforms, healthcare safety",
      description: "Why silver-ion treatments became essential for hospital uniforms.",
      content: `<p class='mb-6'>2020 redefined safety. We discuss how silver-ion fabric treatments provide an extra layer of defense for frontline workers during 12+ hour high-risk shifts.</p>`
    },
    {
      slug: "managing-supply-chain-crisis-2020",
      title: "Resilience: Managing the Supply Chain Crisis of 2020",
      date: "June 15, 2020",
      keywords: "supply chain resilience, manufacturing crisis, medical apparel delivery",
      description: "How Yilong maintained production during a global pandemic.",
      content: `<p class='mb-6'>In a year of total disruption, our vertical integration allowed us to keep deliveries moving. We share the lessons learned in resilience and partner communication.</p>`
    }
  ];

  return posts.map((post) => ({
    params: { slug: post.slug },
    props: { post },
  }));
}

const { post } = Astro.props;
---

<Layout 
  title={`${post.title} | Yilong Scrubs Blog`} 
  description={post.description}
  keywords={post.keywords}
>
  <article class="container mx-auto px-4 py-16 md:py-24 max-w-4xl">
    <a href="/blog" class="text-primary font-bold uppercase text-[10px] md:text-xs tracking-widest hover:underline mb-8 md:mb-12 inline-block italic">← Back to Insights</a>
    
    <header class="mb-12 md:mb-16 text-left">
      <p class="text-xs md:text-sm font-bold text-secondary uppercase tracking-widest mb-4 italic">{post.date}</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black italic text-slate-900 leading-tight mb-8">{post.title}</h1>
      <div class="h-1 w-24 bg-primary mb-12"></div>
    </header>

    <div class="prose prose-lg md:prose-xl prose-slate max-w-none text-slate-700 leading-relaxed italic" set:html={post.content}>
    </div>
    
    <div class="mt-20 pt-10 border-t border-slate-100">
      <div class="bg-slate-900 text-white p-10 md:p-16 rounded-[3rem] text-center shadow-2xl relative overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-8 opacity-10">
           <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-32 h-32" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
             <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-5m-9 0H3m2 0h5M9 7h1m-1 4h1m4-4h1m-1 4h1m-5 10v-5a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v5m-4 0h4" />
           </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-3xl font-black mb-6 italic text-white underline decoration-secondary decoration-4 underline-offset-8">Solve Your Sourcing Headaches</h3>
        <p class="text-xl mb-10 italic text-slate-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Yilong Scrubs has been solving manufacturing pain points since 2006. 10-set MOQs. OEKO-TEX safety. 72/21/7 performance.</p>
        <a href="/contact" class="inline-block bg-primary text-white font-black py-5 px-12 rounded-2xl text-lg uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-blue-800 transition shadow-lg text-center">Work with Yilong Team</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>